  "title": "CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Supervise and coordinate daily construction site activities to ensure timely project progress, enforce safety and quality standards, and communicate effectively with stakeholders to support successful project delivery.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead daily construction site operations to achieve project milestones within scheduled timelines</li><li>Coordinate with workers, subcontractors, and project teams to optimize workflow and resolve operational challenges</li><li>Implement and monitor adherence to safety protocols and quality standards to maintain a secure and compliant work environment</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of 2 years of relevant construction site experience</li><li>Proficient communication skills in English to facilitate effective coordination and reporting</li><li>Ability to work independently with a strong sense of responsibility</li></ul>",
